ergy being from ''[[Space Amoeba]]'' * Melllvar and his mother from ''[[Futurama]]'' * Outsiders from ''[[XCOM: Enemy Unknown]]'' * [[Bill Cipher]] ([[Gravity Falls]]) * The pure intellectuals from the [[Skylark (series)]] * The Novakid Race from the game Starbound. * The Rakshasa is the novel Lord of Light by American author Roger Zelazny, a race of formerly physical beings that "lived in cities" that converted themselves into patterns of energy of that sustain themselves.
